    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to meet the standards of the most demanding purist. The S54 power plant features a fully addressed double-VANOS system and rod bearing service, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with mechanical harmony. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring OEM bushings for surgical turn-in. The ZF 6-speed manual shifts with tactile precision, paired with a perfectly functioning variable M differential. The exterior presents with exceptional paint depth and zero oxidation, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple. This is a turn-key, mechanically superlative example of BMW's finest naturally aspirated era.",
